{
  "stanzas": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "While shepherds watched their flocks by night,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "All seated on the ground,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "The angel of the Lord came down,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "And glory shone around."
        }
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "“Fear nor!” said he- for mighty dread"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Had seized their troubled mind-"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "“Glad tidings of great joy I bring,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "To you and all mankind."
        }
      ],
      "number": 2
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "“To you, in David’s town this day,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Is born of David’s line,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "The Savior who is Christ the Lord;"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "And this shall be the sign:"
        }
      ],
      "number": 3
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "“The heavenly Babe you there shall find"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "To human view displayed,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "All meanly wrapped in swathing bands,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "And in a manger laid.”"
        }
      ],
      "number": 4
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Thus spake the seraph; and forth with"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Appeared a shining throng"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "Of angels praising God on high,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "Who thus addressed their song:"
        }
      ],
      "number": 5
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "“All glory be to God on high,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "And to the earth be peace;"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "Good will henceforth from heaven to men,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "Begin and never cease!”"
        }
      ],
      "number": 6
    }
  ],
  "title": "While Shepherds Watched Their Flocks"
}
